              "description": "Enter an identifier for this condition - **Use _ instead of spa  ces** e.g. 2_hours",
              "showArgument":true,
"argument":"-lab2 ",
              "label":"Condition 2 label (for R plots, use underscore instead of spaces betw  een words)"
